cards.title: Intro
cards.body: This cheat sheet summarizes a reference list of [LaTeX](https://www.latex-project.org/) commonly used display math notation and some application examples of [KaTeX](https://katex.org/).

cards.title: Introduction
cards.body:
[LaTeX](https://www.latex-project.org/) A TEX-based typesetting system suitable for producing scientific, mathematical,
and physical documents of high print quality.

cards.title: Introduction
cards.body: And [KaTeX](https://katex.org/) handles only a smaller subset of LaTeX's mathematical notation for display on the web

cards.body:
